---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About me" mainClass="flex-grow">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">About me</h1>
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Hi, I'm <span class="text-blue-800">Zvonimir.</span></h2>
  <div class="mt-3 flex flex-col space-y-2">
    <p class="text-xl">Whenever you need a website, web app or any problem solved in general, think of me.</p>
    <p class="text-xl">I have several years of professional experience in full-stack development and I'm always looking for new challenges.</p>
    <p class="text-xl">No matter your needs, I can help you achieve your goals with maximum performance and excellence.</p>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8">My skills</h2>
  <div class="mt-3 flex flex-col space-y-2">
    <p class="text-xl">My typical languages of choice are <span class="font-bold">Elixir, TypeScript and JavaScript.</span></p>
    <p class="text-xl">As far as databases go, I'm familiar with several of them, most notably:
    <span class="text-xl font-bold">MySQL, MariaDB, PostgreSQL and Neo4j.</span></p>
    <p class="text-xl">I'm also familiar with several frameworks and libraries, such as:
      <span class="text-xl font-bold">Phoenix, React, Next.js, Express, Nest.js and much more.</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
